amp\":\"2026-03-11T19:00:00Z\",\"event_type\":\"project_created\",\"details\":{{\"project_id\":\"{}\",\"flow\":\"standard\"}}}}\"#,\n            project_id\n        ),\n    ).expect(\"write journal\");\n    fs::write(project_root.join(\"sessions.json\"), r#\"{\"sessions\":[]}\"#).expect(\"write sessions\");","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BNmMHXmrpqphqEoDzMeewD","session_id":"b9859e69-5579-4e82-ac66-49d19cc80e05","uuid":"ba1afc0e-3619-4446-badf-014ee87f7980"}
