{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01N98whSWrtLhK4PoYpdgjru","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UPH8rg6Fv9wdnzQuZau2Jm","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/20260311224813-impl-response-001.md","content":"# Implementation Response (Iteration 1)\n\n## Changes Made\n1. **Durable start/stage boundaries (Required Change 1)**: Reordered the run-start boundary so `run.json` with `Running` status is persisted _before_ `run_started` and `stage_entered` journal events (`engine.rs:172-193`). For stage commits, journal-append or snapshot-write failures after a successful payload/artifact write now: (a) roll back the payload/artifact pair via `remove_payload_artifact_pair`, (b) call `fail_run` to persist `run_failed` journal event and failed snapshot, ensuring no partial durable history is visible (`engine.rs:350-408`). Added `remove_payload_artifact_pair` to `PayloadArtifactWritePort` trait (`service.rs:104-113`) and implemented it in `FsPayloadArtifactWriteStore` (`fs.rs:684-703`).\n\n2. **Final review routing (Required Change 2)**: Changed `BackendRole::for_stage` so `StageId::FinalReview` maps to `CompletionJudge` instead of `Reviewer` (`domain.rs:251`). Updated the `role_mapping_is_deterministic` test assertion to expect `CompletionJudge` for `FinalReview` (`workflow_engine_test.rs:92`).\n\n3. **Failing-port tests (Recommended Improvement)**: Added `FailingJournalStore` and `FailingSnapshotWriteStore` test fakes that delegate to the real FS stores but inject failures on the Nth call. Added two new tests:\n   - `journal_failure_after_payload_rolls_back_and_fails_run` — verifies journal-append failure after payload/artifact write triggers rollback and failed state\n   - `snapshot_failure_after_stage_completed_rolls_back_and_fails_run` — verifies snapshot-write failure after `stage_completed` journal triggers rollback and failed state\n\n## Could Not Address\n- `cargo test` and `cargo clippy` cannot be verified in this environment because `cargo` is not available on `PATH`. All changes were validated through static code review.\n\n## Pending Changes (Pre-Commit)\n- `src/shared/domain.rs` — `FinalReview` now routes to `CompletionJudge`\n- `src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs` — snapshot-first run-start boundary; stage-commit rollback on journal/snapshot failure\n- `src/contexts/project_run_record/service.rs` — added `remove_payload_artifact_pair` to `PayloadArtifactWritePort`\n- `src/adapters/fs.rs` — implemented `remove_payload_artifact_pair` for `FsPayloadArtifactWriteStore`\n- `tests/unit/workflow_engine_test.rs` — updated `FinalReview` role assertion; added failing-port tests\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":220,"cache_read_input_tokens":105751,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":220},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"19a33b10-b5a0-4ba2-8943-a7efa3e34818","uuid":"af7005e3-c4cb-4e4e-8d07-5f8249ab727b"}
