{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_0","type":"agent_message","text":"# Implementation Response (Iteration 1)\n## Changes Made\n- Durable start/stage boundaries:\n  - Reordered run start so `run.json` is written before `run_started` and `stage_entered` journal events.\n  - On stage commit failure after payload/artifact persistence, the engine now removes the payload/artifact pair and calls `fail_run` so a `run_failed` event and failed snapshot are persisted instead of leaving partial durable state.\n\n- Final review routing:\n  - Updated `FinalReview` to map to `CompletionJudge` instead of `Reviewer`.\n  - Adjusted the related test to match the centralized stage-to-role mapping.\n\n- Failure-path test coverage:\n  - Added `FailingJournalStore` and `FailingSnapshotWriteStore`.\n  - Added async tests covering rollback on journal append failure and snapshot write failure.\n\n- Files modified:\n  - `src/shared/domain.rs`\n  - `src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs`\n  - `src/contexts/project_run_record/service.rs`\n  - `src/adapters/fs.rs`\n  - `tests/unit/workflow_engine_test.rs`\n\n## Could Not Address\n- None."}}
